  m_Name: Ergorn Blackbraid
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterName: Ergorn Blackbraid
  portrait: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueLines:
  - 'Hi''ya there Adventurer! '
  - "Welcome to the grand region of Feyr\xFCn! "
  - 'Up ahead is the small town of Eldhavn. '
  - 'Legend has it that ever since the Mother disappeared, everyone in this Universe
    have been shrunken down. '
  - 'It is also said that the Mother possessed a magical gem that, if assembled with
    other runes, could solve any problem a worthy hero would ask of it. '
  - 'Now I was told that it was on the other side of Eldhavn.  '
  - 'Perhaps you should go check in the town if the rumor is real. '
  - 'I''d ask one of the guards at the big ol'' gate at the end of the main road. '
  - 'Maybe they got a bit more information for y''a. '
  - 'Good luck out their pal''. Careful not to trip on the logs! '
